---

---

<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <img 
      src="/images/hero-sunset-cyclists.jpg"
      alt="夕暮れのシルエット、サイクリストたちの旅"
      class="hero-bg-img"
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="badge-icon">🚲</span>
      <span class="badge-text">旅フェス × ツール・ド・ふくしま</span>
      <span class="badge-icon">⛺</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="hero-title animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
      雄大な太平洋を見下ろす<br class="sp-only">絶景の丘で、<br>
      <span class="hero-title-accent">「熱気」と「旅」</span>が<br class="sp-only">交差する。
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-subtitle animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
      極限に挑むレースと、焚き火を囲むキャンプ。<br>
      一見対極にあるふたつの世界が、「自転車」を架け橋にひとつになる。<br class="pc-only">
      旅フェス×自転車レース、楢葉町に誕生。
    </p>

    <div class="hero-meta animate-fade-in-up delay-300">
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="meta-icon">📅</span>
        <span class="meta-text">2026年6月13日(土)・14日(日)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-divider"></div>
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="meta-icon">📍</span>
        <span class="meta-text">福島県楢葉町 天神岬スポーツ公園</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-cta animate-fade-in-up delay-400">
      <a href="https://select-type.com/ev/?ev=WMSza2cQpKQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">
        宿泊予約はこちらから
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#introduction" class="btn-ghost">
        イベントを知る
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-indicator animate-scroll-hint">
    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
      <path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 40%;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.55);
  }

  .hero-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 30%, rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8) 0%, transparent 40%);
  }

  .hero-bg::before,
  .hero-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.3;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-bg::before {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: var(--color-sunset);
    top: -100px;
    right: -100px;
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero-bg::after {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background: var(--color-ocean);
    bottom: -50px;
    left: -50px;
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 960px;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .badge-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .badge-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem);
    color: var(--color-white);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-title-accent {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-sunset), var(--color-sunset-light), var(--color-ocean));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .sp-only {
    display: inline;
  }
  .pc-only {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .sp-only { display: none; }
    .pc-only { display: inline; }
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-meta {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .meta-divider {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .meta-divider { display: block; }
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-sunset), var(--color-coral));
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    z-index: 2;
  }
</style>
